      <h2 id="Carpeta con scripts">Carpeta con scripts<a class="anchor-link" href="#Carpeta con scripts"><img decoding="async" class="link-img" width="24px" height="24px" alt="link image 1" src={svg_paths.link_svg_path}/></a></h2>
