      <h2 id="Declaracion de variables">Declaraci칩n de variables<a class="anchor-link" href="#Declaracion de variables"><img decoding="async" class="link-img" width="24px" height="24px" alt="link image 5" src={svg_paths.link_svg_path}/></a></h2>
